  "body": "**A couple of fine tuning items for the password creation flow:**\r\n\r\n\r\n1a) The description copy underneath the `Create a password` title has been adjusted slightly so it fits more neatly on 2 lines (previously 3 lines). This avoids the red alert text needing to be split over 2 lines. Given that change, the form should be moved up, ensuring the padding between the description and the first input is retained to match the padding we have in place now\r\n\r\n1b) The confirm password input should also house the `show` (eye) icon once the user has entered at least 1 character.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1232\" alt=\"Create a password\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/110033914/9a5b28a1-fced-451c-bf2d-9578eb2d0832\">\r\n\r\n\r\n2a) The additional confirmation step should have the `Confirm your password (again)` input auto-focused\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1232\" alt=\"Confirm password 1\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/110033914/590506ee-42aa-48f4-bf7c-e04edac5b319\">\r\n\r\n\r\n2b) This input should also show the eye icon once the user has entered at least 1 character. \r\n\r\n<img width=\"1232\" alt=\"Confirm password 2\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/110033914/a84720da-a6ec-494a-b136-ed7840209c0f\">\r\n",
